profile:
Windmill Construction has been a Tarion Registered Builder in Ontario since 1997 and have been building quality homes in the Cornwall area for more than 14 years. They specialize in the construction and renovation of residential homes. Windmill Construction offer services such as new home construction, garage construction, additions, and kitchen and bathroom renovations. They provide the overall planning, coordination and control of a project. Windmill Construction believes that customer satisfaction is their number one priority and all builds are above code requirements.
